message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product. It's an exceptional opportunity tailored specifically for individuals like you who appreciate its unique value. I believe it would greatly enhance your capabilities and contribute significantly to your success. Given its worth to you, I propose a price of $9,500 for this product. This offer allows you to acquire it at a premium quality level without breaking the bank. Please let me know if you're interested in discussing further details or finalizing the purchase.
